<Paragraph TextAlignment="Center" FontFamily="Cambria" FontWeight="Bold" FontSize="14">PivotGrid with Context Menu</Paragraph>
<BlockUIContainer>
<TextBlock Style="{DynamicResource HeaderTextStyle}">Features:</TextBlock>
</BlockUIContainer>
<List Margin="20,20,0,0">
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">PivotGrid with context menu over expander cell is displayed.</Paragraph><Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Using the context menu in Grouping Bar, you can dynamically refresh the Grid from bound data and re-arrange items.</Paragraph><Paragraph />
</ListItem>
<ListItem>
<Paragraph FontFamily="Cambria" FontSize="14">Using the context menu in Expander Cell, you can dynamically expand or collapse individual items or an entire field.</Paragraph><Paragraph />
</ListItem>
</List>

